  "title": "",
  "movie": "몬스터 패밀리 (Monster Family)",
  "duration_sec": 649.92,
  "audio_url": "https://pub-7f9ded590f88439d8f48752f6639e723.r2.dev/2020-08-12_screen_english.mp3",
  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.38,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.38,
      "end": 23.0,
      "text": "영화 속 명장면 명대사를 맛깔나게 요리해드립니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 23.4,
      "end": 24.92,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.92,
      "end": 27.14,
      "text": "8월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.14,
      "end": 31.92,
      "text": "David Sofierd의 Happy Family라는 책을 바탕으로 만들어진"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.92,
      "end": 33.26,
      "text": "가족 애니메이션"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.26,
      "end": 34.92,
      "text": "몬스터 패밀리"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.92,
      "end": 37.42,
      "text": "와 굿모닝 크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.42,
      "end": 37.96,
      "text": "굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.96,
      "end": 38.94,
      "text": "굿모닝 로라"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.94,
      "end": 39.74,
      "text": "반갑습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.74,
      "end": 40.46,
      "text": "굿모닝 여러분"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.46,
      "end": 41.36,
      "text": "How are you doing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.72,
      "end": 43.24,
      "text": "I'm doing so-so"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.24,
      "end": 43.9,
      "text": "so-so?"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.08,
      "end": 44.58,
      "text": "좋아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.58,
      "end": 45.56,
      "text": "업그레이될게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.56,
      "end": 46.92,
      "text": "I couldn't be better"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.92,
      "end": 49.24,
      "text": "아 역시 포지티브한"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.24,
      "end": 50.42,
      "text": "I couldn't be better"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.42,
      "end": 51.36,
      "text": "그럼요 그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 51.36,
      "end": 53.8,
      "text": "I'm doing the best I've ever done"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.8,
      "end": 56.16,
      "text": "진짜 다정하신 분 많네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.16,
      "end": 57.44,
      "text": "조금 얄미해 보일 수도 있죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.44,
      "end": 58.6,
      "text": "네 그래요"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.6,
      "end": 60.58,
      "text": "임혜지님께서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.58,
      "end": 63.0,
      "text": "크리스님 정말 다정한 분 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.0,
      "end": 63.8,
      "text": "이렇게 보내주셔가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.5,
      "end": 65.52,
      "text": "오 다정하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.52,
      "end": 65.8,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.8,
      "end": 67.44,
      "text": "Thanks for the compliment"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.44,
      "end": 69.6,
      "text": "네 맞습니다 우리 크리스씨"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.6,
      "end": 70.5,
      "text": "다정하신 분이죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.02,
      "end": 72.72,
      "text": "다정한 편이긴 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.72,
      "end": 72.9,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.9,
      "end": 75.08,
      "text": "우리 저기 가족한테 물어봐야"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.08,
      "end": 76.82,
      "text": "깨끗한 적은 대답 나오지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.82,
      "end": 78.24,
      "text": "오 지난번에 여쭤보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.24,
      "end": 79.8,
      "text": "다정하신 분이라고 하시더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.52,
      "end": 81.5,
      "text": "Who said that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.64,
      "end": 82.3,
      "text": "Your wife?"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.3,
      "end": 82.88,
      "text": "My wife?"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.24,
      "end": 83.6,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.6,
      "end": 84.66,
      "text": "She's so sweet"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.66,
      "end": 85.88,
      "text": "Thank you"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.88,
      "end": 86.2,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.2,
      "end": 88.12,
      "text": "사랑이 가득 넘치는 시간입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.12,
      "end": 88.54,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.04,
      "end": 89.24,
      "text": "자"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.24,
      "end": 91.38,
      "text": "이 영화에 관련되어서요"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.38,
      "end": 92.7,
      "text": "원작 제목이"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.7,
      "end": 94.52,
      "text": "Happy Family이잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.52,
      "end": 95.08,
      "text": "근데"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.08,
      "end": 96.0,
      "text": "Unlike the title"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.0,
      "end": 96.98,
      "text": "The family members"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.98,
      "end": 98.5,
      "text": "looked unhappy"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.5,
      "end": 99.94,
      "text": "Very unhappy"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.94,
      "end": 101.3,
      "text": "A lot of trouble"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.3,
      "end": 102.94,
      "text": "그런 거 보면은"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.94,
      "end": 103.12,
      "text": "이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.12,
      "end": 105.02,
      "text": "Happiness is not far away"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.02,
      "end": 106.58,
      "text": "라는 표현을 우리가 종종 쓰지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.58,
      "end": 108.96,
      "text": "Unhappiness도 마찬가지로"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.96,
      "end": 110.16,
      "text": "Is also not far away"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.16,
      "end": 110.56,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.56,
      "end": 112.18,
      "text": "What's the difference between"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.18,
      "end": 113.76,
      "text": "unhappiness and happiness?"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.02,
      "end": 116.36,
      "text": "It's often very subjective"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.36,
      "end": 116.92,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.92,
      "end": 117.56,
      "text": "So"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.56,
      "end": 118.42,
      "text": "This family"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.42,
      "end": 120.04,
      "text": "It can be unhappy one day"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.04,
      "end": 121.3,
      "text": "And then the next day"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.3,
      "end": 122.14,
      "text": "They may be happy"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.14,
      "end": 122.5,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.5,
      "end": 123.74,
      "text": "It all depends on"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.74,
      "end": 124.06,
      "text": "You know"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.06,
      "end": 124.74,
      "text": "Their mood"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.74,
      "end": 125.96,
      "text": "Circumstances"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.96,
      "end": 126.86,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.86,
      "end": 127.66,
      "text": "그냥"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.66,
      "end": 129.04,
      "text": "They're just normal people"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.04,
      "end": 129.28,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.34,
      "end": 132.5,
      "text": "우리처럼 그냥 보통의 일반적인 사람들입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.5,
      "end": 133.1,
      "text": "그래서"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.1,
      "end": 136.36,
      "text": "그들이 삶을 어떻게 사는지 보면은"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.36,
      "end": 138.52,
      "text": "They're all hard working people"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.52,
      "end": 138.78,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.78,
      "end": 141.46,
      "text": "That's why we can identify with these characters"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.46,
      "end": 141.8,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.8,
      "end": 142.7,
      "text": "They're monsters"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.7,
      "end": 143.28,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.28,
      "end": 145.04,
      "text": "But they're just your average"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.04,
      "end": 147.6,
      "text": "Mom, dad, brother, sister"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.6,
      "end": 148.08,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.08,
      "end": 149.48,
      "text": "They all have their own problems"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.48,
      "end": 152.44,
      "text": "But they need to work them out together"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.44,
      "end": 152.9,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.9,
      "end": 154.16,
      "text": "And love each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.16,
      "end": 154.68,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.68,
      "end": 155.24,
      "text": "We'll see"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.24,
      "end": 156.82,
      "text": "Right now they're not so happy"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.82,
      "end": 158.4,
      "text": "Not happy at all"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.4,
      "end": 160.02,
      "text": "We'll see what happens"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.02,
      "end": 160.48,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.48,
      "end": 161.64,
      "text": "기대가 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.64,
      "end": 163.24,
      "text": "어쨌든"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.24,
      "end": 164.68,
      "text": "행복과 불행은"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.68,
      "end": 165.9,
      "text": "한 끗 차이다라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.9,
      "end": 166.52,
      "text": "메시지를"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.52,
      "end": 167.92,
      "text": "말씀을 먼저 드리면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.92,
      "end": 169.54,
      "text": "오늘 내용 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.54,
      "end": 171.13,
      "text": "Faye"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.13,
      "end": 172.75,
      "text": "We will find the witch"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.75,
      "end": 173.51,
      "text": "I promise"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.51,
      "end": 175.25,
      "text": "It's not just that"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.25,
      "end": 177.51,
      "text": "Finally a boy thought I was pretty"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.51,
      "end": 180.2,
      "text": "And now he can't even look at me"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.2,
      "end": 182.0,
      "text": "Beauty doesn't last"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.0,
      "end": 185.1,
      "text": "It doesn't matter what anyone else thinks, Faye"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.1,
      "end": 187.58,
      "text": "You have to know yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.58,
      "end": 189.0,
      "text": "How special you are"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.0,
      "end": 191.38,
      "text": "You don't need other people to tell you"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.38,
      "end": 195.62,
      "text": "지금 버스 안에 있는 그런 소리가 들리는 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.62,
      "end": 201.66,
      "text": "지금 엠마 가족들을 몬스터로 변하게 하게 한 마녀 바바야가가요"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.66,
      "end": 203.22,
      "text": "바바야가"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.22,
      "end": 205.52,
      "text": "바바야가가 그렇게 마술을 걸었잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.52,
      "end": 206.06,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.06,
      "end": 209.42,
      "text": "She has fled to London"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.42,
      "end": 210.62,
      "text": "She ran away"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.62,
      "end": 211.84,
      "text": "She fled"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.84,
      "end": 213.4,
      "text": "She ran away"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.4,
      "end": 216.44,
      "text": "Apparently she has a little gem"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.44,
      "end": 219.64,
      "text": "And it's the source of her magic power"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.64,
      "end": 221.68,
      "text": "And it ran out of battery"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.68,
      "end": 223.92,
      "text": "Battery 없지만 충전이 필요해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.92,
      "end": 225.08,
      "text": "귀여웠어요 근데"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.08,
      "end": 226.32,
      "text": "It needs to be recharged"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.32,
      "end": 228.06,
      "text": "So she has to go to London"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.06,
      "end": 229.94,
      "text": "To the London Eye"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.94,
      "end": 231.42,
      "text": "Do you know the London Eye?"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.42,
      "end": 233.88,
      "text": "Oh, 이거 Thames 강변에 있는 거잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.88,
      "end": 235.32,
      "text": "Yes, the Thames River"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.32,
      "end": 235.72,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.72,
      "end": 237.68,
      "text": "It's a very famous Ferris wheel"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.68,
      "end": 238.18,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.18,
      "end": 239.14,
      "text": "That you can see"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.14,
      "end": 240.42,
      "text": "If you go on this Ferris wheel"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.42,
      "end": 241.9,
      "text": "You can see all of London"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.9,
      "end": 243.92,
      "text": "Wow, 너무 멋있을 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.92,
      "end": 248.78,
      "text": "이 높이가 한 135m 정도 되는 그런 회전 관람차라고 하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.78,
      "end": 250.66,
      "text": "It used to be the highest point"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.66,
      "end": 251.18,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.18,
      "end": 251.96,
      "text": "In London"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.96,
      "end": 252.58,
      "text": "Not anymore?"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.76,
      "end": 253.42,
      "text": "Not anymore"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.42,
      "end": 255.7,
      "text": "It got beat by some building"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.7,
      "end": 256.2,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.2,
      "end": 257.64,
      "text": "But it used to be the highest point"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.64,
      "end": 258.08,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.08,
      "end": 259.38,
      "text": "And many tourists"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.38,
      "end": 261.6,
      "text": "I think it's still the most popular tourist"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.6,
      "end": 261.9,
      "text": "Yeah, sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.9,
      "end": 262.22,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.22,
      "end": 262.9,
      "text": "Destination"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.9,
      "end": 263.32,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.32,
      "end": 264.66,
      "text": "Or attraction in London"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.66,
      "end": 269.76,
      "text": "아, 영국에 가면 꼭 봐야 되는 그런 상징적인 장소이기도 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.76,
      "end": 271.76,
      "text": "단어들을 좀 살펴볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.38,
      "end": 274.16,
      "text": "Beauty doesn't last"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.16,
      "end": 275.22,
      "text": "That's a sentence"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.22,
      "end": 277.18,
      "text": "아, 이거 완전 중요한 이야기네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.18,
      "end": 279.94,
      "text": "That is a good lesson from mother to daughter"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.94,
      "end": 280.28,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.28,
      "end": 281.38,
      "text": "Beauty doesn't last"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.38,
      "end": 283.54,
      "text": "외모는 한순간이야"
